      "acceptanceCriteria": "Quantitative metric (e.g., E_rms) reported with combined simulation and experimental uncertainty; absolute hemolysis index within acceptance band across all operating points.",
      "rationale": "Predicted hemolysis index deviates from measured values by up to 40% at off-design flow rates. Combined uncertainty analysis performed via Monte Carlo but intervals are wide and do not bound the discrepancy. Achieved level 2 against required level 5."
