      "rationale": "Only the Giersiepen-Wurzinger power-law model was used; no competing model forms were evaluated. Model form uncertainty is unquantified and is a known source of large prediction error in hemolysis CFD. Flagged as epistemic gap at MRL 5; achieved level 1 against required level 5."
